trans-unit.source: Enabling moviemaker mode change the way the game is started (when you click on all "Watch" buttons). It will use the tool "Half-Life Advanced Effects" (HLAE) which is technically a hack. You should use it ONLY if you know what you are doing AND to make moviemaking related stuff. If you don't know what is this or you are not planning to make movies just click on cancel. If you enable it, the game is launched with the "-insecure" parameter (everytime), which means that you will not be able to join server protected by VAC and prevent from a VAC ban.
trans-unit.target: 开启视频作者模式将改变游戏启动方式(当你点击所有"观看"按钮) 这将使用HLACE工具 只有当你知道你在干什么或者做视频时才打开它 如果你不了解这个或者不打算做视频，点击取消 如果你开启了它，游戏每次启动时会伴随"-insucre"启动项，这意味着你将保护你不被VAC封禁并且不能进入VAC保护的服务器
